snippet.title: HITMAN: Sniper Assassin Mode Trailer
snippet.description:
Snipe with your friends or work alone in HITMAN: Sniper Assassin as this new experience will reinforce your natural skill to think deadly.
 
To learn more about HITMAN 2 and Sniper Assassin, please visit www.Hitman.com or join the HITMAN conversation on:
Twitter (@Hitman)  
Facebook (@Hitman)  
Instagram (@Hitman_Official)
YouTube (Hitman)  
Twitch (Hitman)
